# Dependencies (both projects)
**/node_modules/
**/.pnpm-store/

# Build outputs
**/dist/
**/build/

# Logs
**/logs/
**/*.log
**/.manus-logs/

# IDE and editor
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/
*.swp

# OS files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Cache
**/.cache/
**/.parcel-cache/
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Coverage
**/coverage/
**/.nyc_output/

# Environment files (not readable by Claude)
**/.env*
!.env.example

# Binary and document files
*.zip
*.tgz
*.tar.gz
*.gif
*.ico
*.webp
*.mp4
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.svg
*.pdf

# Package manager lock files (large, rarely needed)
**/pnpm-lock.yaml
**/package-lock.json
**/yarn.lock

# Misc
**/tmp/
**/temp/

# Keep CLAUDE.md readable
!**/CLAUDE.md
